    "raw": "Path provenance for content-addressed blobs under shadup `files/`.\n\n## Done\n\n- **Schema:** `stored_files.start` / `.end` (RFC3339); legacy upgrade on open; writes `start=now()`, `end=NULL`; active reads `deleted=0 AND end IS NULL`.\n- **Next in flight:** partial unique index; `shadup mv`.\n\n## Paused after merge\n\n- `shadup reconcile` \u2014 end-date missing paths, start new sightings.\n- Design note + relax index/history semantics if needed.\n- Stop writing `.meta.johan.json` `original-album-name` once DB history suffices.\n\n## mv contract\n\n`shadup mv OLD NEW` renames a file or directory tree on disk (same filesystem) and records DB history: close active row(s) with `end=now()`, open new row(s) with `start=now()`, `end=NULL`. Content hashes unchanged."
  },
